# URL templates and instructional placeholders are not directly fetchable.
\{[^}]+\}
%7B[^%]+%7D

# Private/instructional placeholders.
^https://github\.com/YOUR_USERNAME/

# ETH Zurich SharePoint (private; requires authentication). Pattern catches
# both the personal OneDrive subdomain (ethz-my) and the organisational one
# (ethz), plus any future ethz-* tenant variant.
^https://ethz(-[a-z]+)?\.sharepoint\.com/

# Runtime PDF/download bases. Directory listing is denied; the URL itself
# is not accessible, but the extractor scripts append a filename to fetch
# specific yearbooks. Excluded from CI because the bare base URL fails.
# Manual-check list (build a real filename, paste into a browser, expect
# the PDF to download):
#   - https://hydroproweb.zh.ch/Karten/JB%20GW%20Pegel/Dokumente/
#       Groundwater-level yearbooks (Canton ZH)
#       Filename pattern:  G_<well_id>_<year>.pdf
#       → _SUPPORT/extract_GW_levels_from_yearbooks/yearbook_extractor.py
#   - https://hydroproweb.zh.ch/Karten/B3%20JB%20Wassertemp/Dokumente/
#       River-temperature yearbooks (Canton ZH)
#       Filename pattern:  <station_id>t<yy>.PDF  (e.g. 2099t020.PDF)
#       → _SUPPORT/extract_river_temperature_from_yearbooks/river_temperature_extractor.py
^https://hydroproweb\.zh\.ch/Karten/JB%20GW%20Pegel/Dokumente/$
^https://hydroproweb\.zh\.ch/Karten/B3%20JB%20Wassertemp/Dokumente/$

# Manual-check reminders for runtime data downloads that CURRENTLY pass CI
# (no exclusion regex needed — listed here so a periodic review confirms the
# data product itself is still published in the same shape).
#   - https://data.geo.admin.ch/ch.meteoschweiz.ogd-smn/sma/ogd-smn_sma_d_historical.csv
#       MeteoSchweiz Open Government Data — daily SMA (Zürich/Fluntern)
#       historical air-temperature CSV. Bare directory returns 403; full
#       CSV path returns 200. Verify the file still downloads and the
#       columns (reference_timestamp, tre200d0) haven't changed.
#       → _SUPPORT/extract_river_temperature_from_yearbooks/river_temperature_extractor.py

# Valid scholarly DOI links that currently reject automated CI checks.
# Manual-check list (paste each URL into a browser at each major review):
#   - https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.1317504111
#       Fischhoff & Davis (2014), PNAS              → flow/10_communication.ipynb
#   - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1745-6584.2005.00052.x
#       Anderson (2005), Ground Water               → transport/2_perceptual_model.ipynb
#   - https://doi.org/10.1029/92WR00607
#       Gelhar, Welty & Rehfeldt (1992), WRR        → transport/2_perceptual_model.ipynb
#       NOTE: redirects to agupubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com which bot-blocks
#       (HTTP 403 / Cloudflare challenge) — DOI is canonical & verified.
#       If browser is blocked, verify via Google Scholar:
#       https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=10.1029%2F92WR00607
#   - https://doi.org/10.1146/annurev-statistics-010814-020148
#       Spiegelhalter (2017), Annu. Rev. Statistics → flow/10_communication.ipynb
^https://doi\.org/10\.1073/pnas\.1317504111$
^https://doi\.org/10\.1111/j\.1745-6584\.2005\.00052\.x$
^https://doi\.org/10\.1029/92WR00607$
^https://doi\.org/10\.1146/annurev-statistics-010814-020148$

# Valid ETH Zurich page that returns 415 Unsupported Media Type to
# HEAD requests from CI runner IPs (Cloudflare/WAF bot-detection).
# Browser/local curl returns 200 OK. Manual-check at each major review:
#   - https://innovedumprojects.ethz.ch/projects/groundwater-in-action-real-world-problem-centered-approach-with-students-collaborative-projects/
#       Innovedum project page for this course               → README.md
^https://innovedumprojects\.ethz\.ch/projects/groundwater-in-action-real-world-problem-centered-approach-with-students-collaborative-projects/$
